		"content": {
			"start": 7,
			"end": 252,
			"styles": "\n\t/* `from`/`to` are case-insensitive keyframe-selector keywords; prettier (and\n\t   tsv) lowercase them. Percentage selectors are unaffected. */\n\t@keyframes slide {\n\t\tfrom {\n\t\t\tleft: 0;\n\t\t}\n\t\t50% {\n\t\t\tleft: 50%;\n\t\t}\n\t\tto {\n\t\t\tleft: 100%;\n\t\t}\n\t}\n",
